@startuml sys-score-assistant-attachment-count-guard
!pragma layout smetana
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
    ParticipantPadding 20
    MessageAlign center
}

' ── 對應 BDD Scenario: Attachment count limit is enforced before persistence ──
' ── 契約來源: attachment_contract.puml, grade_record_contract.puml ─────────────

actor "Teacher" as U
participant "AttachmentRestControllerAdapter" as PA <<PrimaryAdapter>>
participant "GradeRecordRepositoryAdapter" as GRSA <<SecondaryAdapter>>
participant "AttachmentRepositoryAdapter" as ATSA <<SecondaryAdapter>>

note over ATSA #EEEEEE
  （本場景中 save() 永不被呼叫）
  AttachmentRepository NOT called — guard blocks persistence.
end note

U -> PA : createAttachment(req: AttachmentRequest)\n[gradeRecordId references a record with 5 attachments]
activate PA

PA -> GRSA : findById(id: UUID)
activate GRSA
GRSA --> PA : Optional<GradeRecord>\n(attachments.size() = 5)
deactivate GRSA

note right of PA
  附件數量上限守衛：
  current attachments (5) >= MAX_ATTACHMENTS (5) ❌
  超出上限，拒絕新增附件。
end note

note over PA #FFCCCC
  ❌ 領域驗證例外拋出
  DomainValidationException
  (Attachment limit exceeded: max 5 per GradeRecord)
  在抵達 AttachmentRepository 之前即拋出例外。
end note

PA -[#red]-> U : ResponseEntity<Void>\n422 Unprocessable Entity (Attachment Limit Exceeded)
deactivate PA

@enduml
